    - The second layer has 2 blocks: a flat block and an angled block on top.

- **Spatial Relationships**:

  - A horizontal yellow rectangular block is placed on top of the four cylindrical blocks.
  - An orange triangle block is leaning on the yellow block, making it appear as a roof.
  - An additional yellow curved block (small semicircle) is on the top of one of the vertical orange blocks.
